}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== A ''Product Equality Declaration letter'' at the FCC says, "difference between FCC ID: :I88WSQ50/I88WSQ60 is antenna type. Other parts are identical to each other." The WSQ60 has "PCB Dipole" antennas while the WSQ50 has "PIFA" antennas. :Most details here are copied from the page for the [[ZyXEL WSQ50]]
